{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-discuss-popular-trends-in-technology/task-5","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-how-to-discuss-popular-trends-in-technology","challengeType":19,"description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>U ovoj izazovu, vežbaćeš ono što si naučio u prethodnim izazovima. Slušaj razgovor i izaberi tačan odgovor.</p>\n</section>","nodules":null,"explanation":null,"helpCategory":"English","instructions":"","fields":{"slug":"/learn/a2-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-discuss-popular-trends-in-technology/task-5"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Koji odgovor najtačnije opisuje veštačku inteligenciju?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Something like a blue sky</span></p>","feedback":"<p>Razgovor ne može biti o svemiru. Zapamti ovu lekciju je o veštačkoj inteligenciji.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Automated Interaction</span></p>","feedback":"<p>U razgovoru se pominju mašine sa veštačkom inteligencijom, ali ne samo za direktnu interakciju. Potraži širu koncepciju.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Something like a smart machine</span></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Advanced Invention</span></p>","feedback":"<p>Koncept naprednog izuma nije pomenut u razgovoru. Razmisli o specifičnoj vrsti inteligencije.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":3}],"scene":{"setup":{"background":"company2-roof.png","characters":[{"character":"Sophie","position":{"x":50,"y":0,"z":1.4},"opacity":0},{"character":"Tom","position":{"x":50,"y":15,"z":1.2},"opacity":0}],"audio":{"filename":"4.2-1.mp3","startTime":1,"startTimestamp":0,"finishTimestamp":21.1},"alwaysShowDialogue":null},"commands":[{"background":null,"character":"Sophie","position":null,"opacity":1,"startTime":0,"fi